p.m:
\displaystyle{\begin{aligned}
    16\cdot\left( -{\frac{1}{8}} \right)
    \amp =\frac{16}{1} \cdot \left(-{\frac{1}{8}}\right) \amp \hbox{We can divide both the first numerator and the second denominator by 8.}\\
    \amp =\frac{2}{1} \cdot \left(-{\frac{1}{1}}\right)\\
    \amp ={-2}
    \end{aligned}}
